{"tid":1175176,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麻疹再現海港城名店　BVLGARI男銷售員中招","createTime":"2019-05-28T11:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T12:21:14.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"430f609c2ee901051d7e0c9bced9a3db2e43a62e","tid":1175176,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T11:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190528/photo/bkn-20190528185924665-0528_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190528192249\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190528%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190528185924665-0528_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190528192249&h=266afe1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀海港城再爆發一宗麻疹個案。衞生署衞生防護中心今日(28日)表示，個案涉及一名32歲男子，過往健康良好，他於上周四(23日)開始發燒和流鼻水，並於上周六(25日)開始出疹，前日(26日)向私家醫生求醫，同日獲轉介到瑪嘉烈醫院急症室求醫，並入院接受治療，病人的呼吸道樣本經檢測後證實對麻疹病毒呈陽性反應。據了解他為名店BVLGARI的店舖銷售員，該店有逾30名員工。 <br />\n<br />\n防護中心表示，病人情況一直穩定。他曾接種兩劑麻疹疫苗，於潛伏期及病毒傳染期內均沒有外遊。根據病人提供的資料，他於潛伏期內沒有接觸麻疹病人，其家居接觸者至今沒有出現病徵，並正接受醫學監察。 <br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心接獲該確診個案通報後，隨即展開流行病學調查，並已進行接觸者追蹤的工作，調查仍然繼續。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190528/bkn-20190528185924665-0528_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190528%2Fbkn-20190528185924665-0528_00822_001.html&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2A4SWcZegttS7JwdJctbizM%3D&h=d768a376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190528/bkn-20190528185924665-0528_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3ae0200bd3ed85028f360de36572966d2f588f20","tid":1175176,"uid":187956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T11:36:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />麻疹城"},{"pid":"92770c36006c2a2c274fbd7c75b142bff686c4b2","tid":1175176,"uid":83251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T11:40:11.000Z","msg":"大陸客送大禮?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33fd5fc555e92097adf96fd0ac8ee173d8fc84fc","tid":1175176,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T11:40:42.000Z","msg":"抵死，支那狗場"},{"pid":"257996eee48fa619d853f4076d76882c3bc55598","tid":1175176,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:01:51.000Z","msg":"支那城"},{"pid":"3f01d7a6a44113d3e06c5d3f685559532c104bf1","tid":1175176,"uid":66527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:11:58.000Z","msg":"支那送大禮"},{"pid":"db3b15a4b84534b9dc1bcc0084950c4a468208f8","tid":1175176,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:20:29.000Z","msg":"狗倉或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"d2bc678737872077e518ec8911f7d20b91bca08f","tid":1175176,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:21:14.000Z","msg":"有病假放 , 正啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}